<section>

  <h3>Never miss a streamed set.</h3>

  <p>
    Add Setbot to your Discord server and get notified anytime your favorite
    players have a set on a major tournament stream.
  </p>

  <p>
    Also useful for players with their own Discord servers who want to
    automatically ping their followers whenever their sets are on stream.
  </p>

  <p>
    <a
      href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1358490190188122162"
      target="_blank"
      class="button"
    >Add to Server</a>
  </p>

</section>

<section>

  <h3>Setup</h3>

  <p>
    Give Setbot
    <b>View Channel</b>,
    <b>Send Messages</b>,
    <b>Manage Messages</b>, and
    <b>Read Message History</b>
    permissions in the channel where you want sets to be announced.
  </p>

  <p>
    Type
    <b>/connect</b>
    in the channel with the tag of the player you want to follow.
  </p>

  <p>
    After the connection is set up, optionally select a role to ping with each
    set announcement.
  </p>

  <p>
    That's it! If you run into any issues, get help in the
    <b>#setbot</b>
    channel
    <a href="https://discord.gg/x7E38ygc42" target="_blank">in Discord</a>.
  </p>

</section>
